{"tid":273664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魯迅曾說：「我們極容易變成奴隸，而且變了之後，還萬分喜歡。」","createTime":"2017-06-06T17:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T03:16:07.000Z","uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac87b31ce771f42068e80535a6052e654bcc582","tid":273664,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"這話用在如今香港的某些人身上，實在太貼切了，&hellip;&hellip;對國家民族文化歷史一無所知，但為了某些利益，忽然愛國，奴性盡現，還萬分欣喜。<br />\n<br />\n如果從奴性生活中找出特點來，應該是讚嘆、揣摩、陶醉，時刻讚嘆主子的偉大，絞盡腦汁揣摩主子的心意，陶醉在主子施捨的榮耀中。"},{"pid":"c52cf863b666b80f9562ff608a2745e882ad1131","tid":273664,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"雖然好認同，但出處？"},{"pid":"eb08b6acc46b584b72289b0e9387e289a3274da8","tid":273664,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:10:16.000Z","msg":"魯迅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8ed780f9a530fccef1e64f585f8cf078a700a3","tid":273664,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}